            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The apprentice magicians launch shards of pure magic at all creatures in a 10-foot burst within 120 feet. This barrage deals 5d4 force damage (DC 19 basic Reflex save). When the clique is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a 5-foot burst.",
